                            </div>
                        </amp-lightbox>
                    </div>
                    <!-- /margin -->

                    <div class="margin">
                      <h4>Step 2</h4>
                      <p>
                        Click the Movement block labeled <strong>That are</strong>: to display options for selecting where in the video that object is and how it is moving. Select the location and/or direction of the object you wish to find (e.g., inside or outside a region, crossing a boundary, coming in or out of a door).
                      </p>
                      <br>
                      <div>
                          <amp-img on="tap:lightbox6" role="button" tabindex="0" src="/images/Sighthound_06.png" width="999" height="743" layout="responsive" class="shadow"></amp-img>
