                          </div>
                      </amp-lightbox>
                    </div>
                    <!-- /margin -->

                    <div class="margin">
                      <h4>Step 3</h4>
                      <p>Click the Response block labeled <strong>If Seen</strong>: to display options for an alarm responses and the video recording storage management.</p>
                      <br>
                      <div>
                          <amp-img on="tap:lightbox7" role="button" tabindex="0" src="/images/Sighthound_07.png" width="999" height="743" layout="responsive" class="shadow"></amp-img>
